column5: Here you have some of the best pikes I got this last June.            The weather was just perfect for pike fishing, cool temperatures and cloudy days most of the time. A pity that July has come with hot and sun, hope the situation changes soon.  Hope you enjoy the pictures.
Some very nice fish there, Hauki. Thank you for sharing.
Where in ontario is "Finland"? I can't find it on my map anywhere  Great looking fish.  Thanks for the adventure
Nice pike. Jeez. I might be a tad intimidated coming eyeball to eyeball with pike that size up to my chest their water.  JF
Nice gators Hauki Thanks for sharing Leechman
I REALLY need to get a passport then start saving to get to get to Finland!!!!!  vance
Hyvin tehty ystäväni.  You are making me so jealous.
Nice to see you waist deep searching for Pike and some really nice specimens....right on!!!!  More Essox from your future outings would be great. Thanks for sharing.
Great pics and some hawg gators for sure .
Nice fish. Wading for big Northerns, now that is cool.
